HEADWORD: Plumbagin
<hw>Plum*ba"gin</hw> <pr>(pl⟦ucr⟧m*b⟦amac⟧"j⟦icr⟧n)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[L. <ets>plumbago</ets> leadwort, fr. <ets>plumbum</ets> lead; cf.
F. <ets>plombagin</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>A crystalline
substance said to be found in the root of a certain plant of the
Leadwort (<gen>Plumbago</gen>) family.</def>⟦br⟧
